{"tid":2067400,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民建聯盧文端　要求 DQ 反對「港區國安法」人士　禁參選立法會","createTime":"2020-06-17T03:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T05:20:55.000Z","uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"371622b6f6c46723e3fb7ab45e339346a3f3b439","tid":2067400,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screenshot202020-06-1720at2011.02.0820AM_EQVcQ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreenshot202020-06-1720at2011.02.0820AM_EQVcQ_1200x0.png&h=a390b2a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n盧文端<br />\n前政協委員、民建聯監委會主席盧文端今天在《明報》撰文，指反對「港區國安法」的泛民立法會參選人，都應該被 DQ （取消參選資格）。<br />\n<br />\n身兼國僑聯副主席、中國和平統一促進會香港總會理事長的盧文端，指香港雖然容許表達反對港區國安法，但必須劃清界限：不適用於立法會參選人。他指，立法會議員和公職人員都是特區建制的重要組成部分，都是「屬於建制人士」，權利和義務必須對等，既然議員「享受進入特區建制」當公職人員的權利，就要承擔公職人員宣誓擁護特區政府的義務，稱這無關言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n他接著指，參選立法會的人同特定公職人士一樣，不可以表態反對港區國安法，若泛民人士想跟普通香港市民一樣，擁有表達反對港區國安法的「言論自由」，大可以選擇在建制以外，不參選立法會。<br />\n<br />\n文章又批評有言論指，中央大舉 DQ 反對港區國安法的參選人會激起社會更大的反抗，這種恐嚇性的講法對中央同特區政府都影響不大，又說即使面對國際大反彈，中央都不為所動，面對香港反對派更加不可能退讓。<br />\n<br />\n盧文端又指，以往泛民以建制的議會平台，肆意發表反對維護國家安全的主張，促使危害國家安全言論在香港大行其道，在中央立港區國安法之後，一定要剝去反對維護國家安全言論的「正當性」，第一步就是禁止反對國安法的人進入議會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%A7%E6%96%87%E7%AB%AF-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82-dq-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-%E7%A6%81%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%25A7%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25AB%25AF-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582-dq-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=c0a41d29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%25A7%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25AB%25AF-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582-dq-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%2F&h=2a680af7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%A7%E6%96%87%E7%AB%AF-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82-dq-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-%E7%A6%81%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83/</a>"},{"pid":"fcb018e9cf823222df539c4a4c752a964f612aa3","tid":2067400,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"快！唔做正契弟！"},{"pid":"9f1e18bbc8adec4122bf992ec8c2dad737502365","tid":2067400,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"73c586014194df0cdebb1eba64f8843936f68a8b","tid":2067400,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:32:01.000Z","msg":"盧文端手足嚟<br />\n<br />\n就係佢搞中環中心事件，一野燒乾福建幫資金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c718f11bdaa58d5ae8a5cad0f3ad168e8f7ea7b8","tid":2067400,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:32:03.000Z","msg":"快啲做<br />\n拆散晒香港套嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c095cfa7540e4ef2b929e472d29bf69333cd9b9","tid":2067400,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T0